    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311540/extras/99ac19bb5152b3820752817dd877f5dc.avif?t=1728624061\" width=620 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《浪痕：回忆密码》是游戏开发者 Somi “负罪感三部曲”的最后一部，前作分别是 Replica（《指尖战争》）和 Legal Dungeon（《律法之地》）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311540/extras/245cb2c9b68d92aed33b8425c8404337.poster.avif?t=1728624061\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311540/extras/245cb2c9b68d92aed33b8425c8404337.webm?t=1728624061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1311540/extras/245cb2c9b68d92aed33b8425c8404337.mp4?t=1728624061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>倘若让我简短地概括自己的一生，我会说，“我说的一切都是谎言。”</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在爷爷的三天葬礼上，一道陈年的伤疤被揭开，那是一切愧疚感的源头。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一本记录了祖孙三代回忆与他们间感情纠葛的日记。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这本日记的部分内容使用简易替换密码进行了加密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家只有在破译之后才能获悉真相，并感受作者埋藏在字里行间的深沉情感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这本日记的内容影射着作者矛盾的一生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >船只驶过，留下浪痕，那是被世代相承的残酷诅咒吞噬的一生。</p>",
